            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding bg-dark-card">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-64">
          <span class="eyebrow">Core Values</span>
          <h2 class="section-heading">What I Stand For</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3-col">
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <!-- <span class="material-symbols-outlined">loyalty</span> -->
            </div>
            <h4>Integrity</h4>
            <p>
              Honest advice and fair pricing. If a repair isn't necessary, I'll
              tell you. Trust is the foundation of my business.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <!-- <span class="material-symbols-outlined">architecture</span> -->
            </div>
            <h4>Precision</h4>
            <p>
              Millimeter-perfect assembly and meticulous pruning. I pay
              attention to the details that others often overlook.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <!-- <span class="material-symbols-outlined">cleaning_services</span> -->
            </div>
            <h4>Cleanliness</h4>
            <p>
              I respect your space. I arrive on time and leave your home cleaner
              than I found it, every single time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-banner">
          <h2 class="cta-title">Ready for your next project?</h2>
